name: Featherless Parrotbrain
author: @larskristo
description: In crimson eyes, a haunting gaze penetrates the soul. Spectral whispers echo through the mind, a chilling embrace of the macabre.

name: Count Jesusla
author: @larskristo
description: Phantasmal visage emerges from shadows deep, A spectral portrait, a haunting soul to keep. Eyes hollow, yet piercing through the veil of night, In darkness eternal, a chilling, unsettling sight.

name: Father Sin
author: @larskristo
description:
A weathered visage, etched with dark intent,
Piercing gaze, a soul's torment.
In eyes once bright, now shadows creep,
Secrets of the abyss, forever to keep.

name: Mother Virtue
author: @larskristo
description: A ghastly visage emerges from the abyss, eyes ablaze with eldritch malice. Its twisted countenance, a portrait of unspeakable horror, whispers dark secrets from beyond the veil.

name: Pheolix
author: @larskristo
description:
In the void's embrace, a specter blooms,
Crimson petals unfurl, a haunting tome.
Shadows whisper secrets, dark and deep,
Of forgotten souls in eternal sleep.

name: Cathomet
author: @larskristo
description: In the twilight's gloom, a spectral owl looms, Piercing gaze ensnares the soul, a haunting tomb. Feathered shadows unfurl, wisdom's eerie sight, Ancient whispers echo through the darkest night.
